OL,3,CMan charged with murder of woman in
OL,4,CStoke-on-Trent
OL,6,FA man has been charged with murder
OL,7,Fafter a woman was found dead in Stoke-
OL,8,Fon-Trent.
OL,10,FEmergency services were called to an
OL,11,Faddress in Oakwell Court, in Longton,
OL,12,Fat around 3.30am on Sunday, 12 July.
OL,14,F24-year-old Sarah-Louise Pennington
OL,15,Fwas found dead inside.
OL,17,F30-year-old Kyle Pala from Stoke-on-
OL,18,FTrent was arrested and has been
OL,19,Fcharged with murder.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G1/2
