OL,3,CMan charged with murder of woman in
OL,4,CStoke-on-Trent
OL,6,FPala remains in custody and is due to
OL,7,Fappear at the North Staffordshire
OL,8,FJustice Centre today (July 15th).
OL,10,FStaffordshire Police say scene
OL,11,Fenquiries in the area are continuing
OL,12,Fbut they are working to minimise the
OL,13,Fdisruption to local residents.
